card.description: Companies have announced billions in new investments in the United States while President Donald Trump has been traveling and signing deals in the Middle East this week.The president has traveled to Saudi Arabia, Qatar, and the United Arab Emirates so far this week to sign agreements and receive commitments that will generate roughly $2 trillion in trade and investment.
